  "Human": "人类",
  "Starting Boost: Presence +1\nHeirs to the great Belharan Empire of ages past, humans have spread across the world in spite of their short lives. Theirs is a race that is ever expanding, ever-growing and learning. It is no wonder some would come to the far reaches of the north, seeking new land and new adventures. Humanity's boundless ambitions lend to greater Presence.": "起始加成：魅力 +1\n人类是昔日伟大贝拉汉帝国的继承者，尽管寿命短暂，却已遍布世界。这个种族不断扩张、成长与学习。因此有人来到北方最远处，寻找新土地和新冒险也就不足为奇了。人类无尽的野心带来了更高的魅力。",
  "Lupine": "卢平人",
  "Starting Boost: Strength +1\nTall and powerful, the lupines of the north are descended from lycans and bear thick body fur resembling that of a gray or arctic wolf. Natives of the region, lupines spent several years fighting against the encroaching human presence before being forced to accept defeat, and their new neighbors. Their physiques lend them to higher Strength than other races.": "起始加成：力量 +1\n高大强壮的北方卢平人是狼人的后裔，身上覆有灰狼或北极狼般的厚毛。作为当地原住民，卢平人曾与不断蚕食的人类战斗多年，最终被迫接受失败并接纳新邻居。他们的体格赋予其比其他种族更高的力量。",
  "Catfolk": "猫人",
  "Starting Boost: Agility +1\nLithe and agile denizens of the endless forests of the north, catfolk are the most sociable of the beast-kin and were eager to join elves and men in society when they were first met in the great deserts of the Southlands. Catfolks' friendliness often underlies a cheeky mischievous streak. Their grace and dexterity give them a naturally higher Agility.": "起始加成：敏捷 +1\n猫族是北方无尽森林中轻盈敏捷的居民，是兽族中最善交际的。当他们在南方大陆的大沙漠中首次与精灵和人类相遇时，便热切地加入了社会。猫族的友善之下常藏着顽皮狡黠的一面。他们的优雅与灵巧使其天生拥有更高的敏捷。",
  "Wyld Elf": "远古精灵",
  "Starting Boost: Willpower +1\nA fey race possessed of an otherworldly grace, wyld elves have a preternatural connection to nature and magic. They all have a feminine appearance, regardless of actual sex (with some males even sporting breasts), and each elf manifests a mark of the wyld, such as animalistic ears or bestial tails. Their inherent grasp of magic grants wyld elves a bonus to Willpower.": "起始加成：意志 +1\n作为拥有超凡优雅的精类种族，远古精灵与自然和魔法有着超自然的联系。不论实际性别，他们都外表女性化（有些男性甚至长有乳房），且每个精灵都会显现荒野印记，比如兽耳或兽尾。他们对魔法的天生掌握让远古精灵获得意志加成。",
  "Orc": "兽人",
  "Starting Boost: Toughness +1\nTowering, brawny barbarians with green skin and bestial tusks, orcs are savage raiders that hail from the craggy foothills of the north. Few of them voluntarily join civilization, preferring their tribal lives under the command of powerful warlords. Their naturally thick hides and an ingrained warrior tradition grants them bonus Toughness.": "起始加成：坚韧 +1\n兽人是高大强壮、绿皮肤、长獠牙的野蛮掠夺者，来自北方嶙峋的丘陵地带。他们很少自愿融入文明社会，更愿意在强大酋长的带领下过部落生活。他们天生的厚皮与根深蒂固的战士传统给予他们额外的坚韧。",
  "Who you are, where you come from, and what you know, are determined by your background.\n\nBackgrounds will increase your starting attributes, and many events in the story will change — often subtly, but sometimes in significant ways — due to the knowledge and training inherent to your background.\n\nWho are you, and where did you start before your year of adventure and travel?": "你的身份、你的出身以及你的知识都由你的背景决定。\n\n背景会提升你的初始属性，许多事件会因你背景中的知识和训练而改变——有时是微妙的，有时则是显著的。\n\n你是谁？在冒险与旅行开始之前，你从哪里出发？",
  "Noble Scion": "贵族后裔",
  "Starting Boost: Presence +1\nYou're the youngest child of a noble family, with all the pampering and prestige that entails — not to mention training in arts of magic or battle to your hearts' content. As the youngest child, though, you had little hope of inheriting power and so now seek your own fortunes on the frontier. Your noble upbringing imparts a bonus to Presence.": "起始加成：魅力 +1\n你是贵族家庭中最年幼的孩子，自小受尽宠爱与尊崇——更别说随心所欲地学习魔法或战斗技艺。然而作为幼子，继承权力的希望渺茫，你只好前往边境寻找自己的财富。你的贵族教养让你获得魅力加成。",
  "Hunter": "猎人",
  "Starting Boost: Agility +1\nYou were born and raised in the wilderness of the northlands, surviving by your skill with a bow and your attunement with nature. Like you, your parents were adventurers, and left early in your life. You're used to living alone — you're quick, quiet, and fleet of foot after years of living in arboreal solitude. Your life as a hunter has given you greater Agility.": "起始加成：敏捷 +1\n你在北地的荒野中出生并长大，靠着弓箭技巧和与自然的调谐生存。和你一样，你的父母也是冒险者，在你年幼时就离开了。你早已习惯独居——在森林中隐居多年让你变得迅捷、安静、脚下生风。猎人的生活赋予你更高的敏捷。",
  "Scholar": "学者",
  "Starting Boost: Cunning +1\nYou were trained in the highest institutes of education in the south, which emulate the legendary colleges of ancient Belhar. The constraints of academia grated against you, however, and eventually you had to strike out on your own. Your rich classical education covered the basics of all manner of scholarly pursuits and the secrets of magic, granting a bonus to your Cunning.": "起始加成：狡黠 +1\n你曾在南方的最高学府受教，这些学府效仿古代贝拉汉的传奇学院。然而学术的束缚让你渐生不满，最终不得不独自出走。你丰富的古典教育涵盖各种学术研究的基础和魔法的秘密，让你获得狡黠加成。",
  "Soldier": "士兵",
  "Starting Boost: Strength +1\nThe life of a soldier in the ruins of the Belharan Empire is hard and brutal, requiring constant physical fitness and training. You've served in conflicts against monsters and barbarians, and now bring your skills and experiences from the frontlines to the frontier. Your rigorous training has given you a bonus to Strength.": "起始加成：力量 +1\n在贝拉汉帝国的废墟中当一名士兵，生活艰苦而残酷，需要持续的体能锻炼和训练。你曾参与对抗怪物和野蛮人的战斗，现在将前线的技能与经验带到边疆。你严格的训练让你获得力量加成。",
  "Courtesan": "交际花",
  "Starting Boost: Presence +1\nYou were a high-class escort in one of the up-and-coming metropolises of the south, always in demand and paid handsomely for your services. You've done it all, with everyone. However, an affair with a powerful noble whose spouse turned against you caused you to flee the city and seek the anonymity of the frontier. Your charisma and manipulative skills increase your Presence.": "起始加成：魅力 +1\n你曾是南方一座新兴大都市的高级陪侍，总是供不应求，报酬丰厚。你阅人无数，无所不为。然而一次与某权贵的私情被其配偶发现，逼得你逃离城市，前往边境寻求隐姓埋名的生活。你的魅力与手腕增加了你的魅力。",
  "Minstrel": "吟游诗人",
  "Starting Boost: Presence +1\nOnce apprenticed to one of the greatest bards in your homeland, you struck out on your own to share your songs and stories across the far frontier. Your career in showmanship has taught you to inspire people and bring them to believe your words and songs, imparting a bonus to Presence.": "起始加成：魅力 +1\n你曾在家乡一位最伟大的吟游诗人门下学徒，之后独自出发，将你的歌谣与故事传到遥远的边疆。你的表演生涯教会你如何鼓舞人心，让他们相信你的言语和歌曲，为你带来魅力加成。",
  "Arcanist": "奥术师",
  "Starting Boost: Willpower +1\nYou were apprenticed to a hedge witch, a powerful and beautiful enchantress living in the depths of the wilderlands southwest of the Frost Marches. You split on bad terms, forcing you to seek your own fortunes. Your tutelage under the witch has given you a mastery of magic, boosting your Willpower.": "起始加成：意志 +1\n你曾师从一位野地女巫，一位住在霜雾沼泽西南荒野深处、强大而美丽的女术士。你们不欢而散，迫使你自谋生路。在女巫门下的学习让你掌握了魔法，增强了你的意志。",
  "Barbarian": "野蛮人",
  "Starting Boost: Toughness +1\nYou're a barbarian, a savage wildling from beyond the borders of civilization. Though your tribe exemplified the warrior's code of honor and bravery, that did not save them from the orcish raiders who wiped them out. Only you survived, forced to seek out a new life beyond your clan's homelands. Your barbarian prowess grants a bonus to Toughness.": "起始加成：坚韧 +1\n你是一名野蛮人，来自文明边界之外的野性蛮族。虽然你的部族恪守着战士的荣誉与勇气准则，但这未能让他们免于兽人掠夺者的屠戮。只有你活了下来，被迫在故土之外寻找新生。你的野蛮人力量让你获得坚韧加成。",
  "Slum Rat": "贫民窟老鼠",
  "Starting Boost: Agility +1\nYou were born in the gutter. Your mother was a whore, and you've been existing in the dregs of society ever since you took your first breath. You've stolen, seduced, and fought tooth and nail to survive. Tiring of life in the city of your birth, not to mention the growing demands of the Thieves' Guild, you've set out to make your fortunes in the Frost Marches. Your thieving experience gives you a boost to Agility.": "起始加成：敏捷 +1\n你生在阴沟里。你母亲是个娼妓，自你呱呱坠地起，你便活在社会的渣滓中。你偷过、骗过、拼死挣扎只为活下来。厌倦了出生城市的生活，更别提盗贼公会越来越高的要求，你动身前往霜雾沼泽寻找财富。你的盗贼经验提高了你的敏捷。",
  "Acolyte": "侍僧",
  "Starting Boost: Willpower +1\nYou were raised in a monastery of the Living Gods, trained in religious ceremony, scholarly pursuits, and the ways of healing magics. You eventually left your order to bring your knowledge and skills to the frontier, eager to help those far from the light of civilization. Your magical training grants you a bonus to Willpower.": "起始加成：意志 +1\n你在一所活神修道院长大，接受宗教仪式、学术研究和治疗魔法的训练。你最终离开了修会，将你的知识与技能带往边疆，渴望帮助那些远离文明之光的人。你的魔法训练让你获得意志加成。",

  "Warrior": "战士",
  "Thief": "盗贼",
  "White Mage": "白魔法师",
  "Black Mage": "黑魔法师",
  "Charmer": "魅术师",
  "Primary Attribute: Toughness\nClass Affinities: Toughness, Strength, Agility\nMasters of armed combat, warriors live and die by their martial skill and the strength of their armor. As a warrior, you will be unparalleled at enduring enemy attacks and drawing their ire from your more vulnerable companions. A strong heart and raw toughness will see you through the dangers you face more than anything else, supported by your capacity to strike with great strength and agility when the going gets rough. The life of a warrior is one of triumph through violence.": "主要属性：坚韧\n职业属性：坚韧、力量、敏捷\n武力大师，战士的生死取决于他们的武艺和盔甲的强度。作为战士，你将无与伦比地承受敌人攻击，并从较弱的同伴那里激怒敌人。坚强的内心和原始的韧性将助你度过最危险的时刻，这也得益于你在艰难时刻以极强的力量和敏捷出击。战士的生活是通过暴力取得胜利的。",
  "Primary Attribute: Agility\nClass Affinities: Agility, Cunning, Strength\nAdepts of shadow and subterfuge, thieves make their fortunes in the underbellies of distant cities and on the lonely trade roads with equal ease. As a thief, you're hard to pin down and hit, easily evading enemy attacks before slipping behind them for the kill. Agility is your greatest weapon — both for avoiding harm, and landing your own blows — however, having the cunning to pick out your enemies' weaknesses and the strength to exploit them are valuable assets indeed. The life of a thief is one of profit through swiftness and guile.": "主要属性：敏捷\n职业属性：敏捷、狡诈、力量\n盗贼擅长阴影与诡计，在遥远城市的底层和孤独的贸易路上轻松发财。作为盗贼，你很难被锁定和击中，能轻松躲避敌人攻击，然后悄悄绕到敌人身后完成致命一击。敏捷是你最强的武器——无论是躲避伤害还是命中自己——但能洞察敌人弱点并加以利用的力量，确实是宝贵的优势。小偷的生活是通过迅速和狡诈谋取利润。",
  "Primary Attribute: Willpower\nClass Affinities: Willpower, Toughness, Presence\nScholars of the occult who dedicate themselves to the healing and preservation of others, white mages study the magic granted to mortals by the gods long ago. As a white mage, you can use your magic to shield your allies from harm, heal their wounds, and to attune with nature for your defense. Maintaining the willpower to harness and control your magic is critical, but in the dangerous Frost Marches, you'll rely on your toughness and presence more and more to keep your party together. The life of a white mage is one of dedication to your comrades and those you deem worthy of your protection.": "主要属性：意志力\n职业属性：意志力、坚韧、存在感\n白魔法师是致力于治愈和保护他人的神秘学者，研究神明早已赐予凡人的魔法。作为白魔法师，你可以用魔法保护盟友免受伤害，治疗他们的伤口，并与自然调和以防御。保持驾驭和控制魔法的意志力至关重要，但在危险的冰霜行军中，你将越来越依赖坚韧和存在感来维系队伍。白魔法师的生活是对战友和你认为值得保护的人的奉献。",
  "Primary Attribute: Willpower\nClass Affinities: Willpower, Cunning, Presence\nScholars of the occult who delve into the twisted, and often forbidden, secrets left behind by the Wraiths that once plagued the world are referred to \"black mages\" by more traditional sorcerers. As a black mage, you command tremendous magical power, able to blast your foes with magic, corrupt their minds, or even bind spirits to do your bidding. You must have great willpower to control such magics, though, and you'll need both cunning to resist the temptations and dangers of magic, and the presence to overbear and command dangerous spirits. The life of a black mage is one of power through knowledge and secrets.": "主要属性：意志力\n职业属性：意志力、狡诈、存在感\n那些深入研究幽灵族留下、常常被禁止的扭曲秘密的学者，被更传统的巫师称为“黑魔法师”。作为黑魔法师，你拥有强大的魔力，能用魔法轰击敌人，腐蚀他们的心智，甚至束缚灵体服从你的命令。不过，你必须有强大的意志力才能控制这些魔法，同时还需要狡猾来抵抗魔法的诱惑和危险，同时还需要有气场来压制和指挥危险的灵体。黑魔法师的生活是通过知识和秘密获得力量的。",
  "Primary Attribute: Presence\nClass Affinities: Presence, Agility, Cunning\nWhile the world is full of bards and performers, only some of these rare souls learn to blend magic and sensuality together into a unique performance that inspires lust and courage. As a charmer, you know how to bolster the courage and fighting spirit of your companions, and how to sap the wills of those who oppose you. Song, spell, and your sensual body are all means to your ends. Your presence — your innate and irresistible force of personality — is your greatest weapon, supplemented by the agility of a charmer and the cunning to both manipulate and resist the wiles of others. The life of a charmer is one of joy sought in the hearts of others.": "主要属性：存在感\n职业属性：存在感、敏捷、狡诈\n虽然世界上充满吟游诗人和表演者，但只有少数罕见的灵魂学会将魔法与感官融合，呈现出激发欲望与勇气的独特表演。作为魅惑者，你知道如何增强同伴的勇气和战斗精神，也知道如何削弱反对者的意志。歌唱、咒语和你那感官的身体都是达成目的的手段。你的存在感——你天生且不可抗拒的个性力量——是你最强大的武器，再加上魅力者的敏捷和操控与抵抗他人诡计的狡猾。魅惑者的生活充满了在他人心中寻求的喜悦。",

